Folder: academy-fee-system/

index.html (Login Page)

Simple email/password form.

Redirects to admin.html or teacher.html based on role.

teacher-dashboard.html

Add Student Modal: Form to input Name, Phone, Fee, Date (Write Only).

Student List: Shows only Name & Paid/Pending Status (Read Only).

Action: "Mark Paid" button (Inserts row into payments table).

admin-dashboard.html

Full access. See total revenue, phone numbers, edit fees.

Branch management controls.

style.css

Mobile-first CSS (Large buttons, readable fonts for phone screens).

supabase-client.js

Contains your createClient initialization and standard DB functions (e.g., addStudent, markPaid).

app.js

Handles the logic: checking if user is logged in, fetching data from the View, and handling the "Add Student" form submission.
